headline: Colgate-Palmolive earnings, consumer sentiment: What to Watch
summary: Here's what investors are watching on Friday, April 25. Colgate-Palmolive (CL), SLB (SLB), Charter Communications (CHTR), and AbbVie (ABBV) are set to report earnings. The final consumer sentiment estimate for April will be released in the morning with economists expecting 50.6, a slight decline from 50.8. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.

headline: AbbVie Submits Biologics License Application to U.S. FDA for TrenibotulinumtoxinE (TrenibotE) for the Treatment of Glabellar Lines
summary: AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) today announced submission of a Biologics License Application (BLA) to the U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) for trenibotulinumtoxinE (TrenibotE) for the treatment of moderate to severe glabellar lines.
